{
    "chapter": 89,
    "verses": {
        "1": {
            "verses": {
                "89:1": {
                    "id": 1
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>清高真主以黎明盟誓，</p>"
        },
        "2": {
            "verses": {
                "89:2": {
                    "id": 2
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>以伊历十二月的前十夜盟誓，</p>"
        },
        "3": {
            "verses": {
                "89:3": {
                    "id": 3
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>以事物的双数和单数盟誓，</p>"
        },
        "4": {
            "verses": {
                "89:4": {
                    "id": 4
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>以来临、逗留、逝去的夜晚盟誓，这些盟誓的答案是‘我必将依你们的行为报酬你们！’</p>"
        },
        "5": {
            "verses": {
                "89:5": {
                    "id": 5
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>上述盟誓能说服有智之士吗？</p>"
        },
        "6": {
            "verses": {
                "89:6": {
                    "id": 6
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>使者啊！难道你没有看到你的主是怎样惩罚否认他们使者胡德的族人阿德人的吗？</p>"
        },
        "7": {
            "verses": {
                "89:7": {
                    "id": 7
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>阿德人部落的祖先属高大的伊赖姆人。</p>"
        },
        "8": {
            "verses": {
                "89:8": {
                    "id": 8
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>真主在这个地区没有创造如他们一样的人，</p>"
        },
        "9": {
            "verses": {
                "89:9": {
                    "id": 9
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>难道你没有看到你的主是怎样惩罚撒立哈的族人赛莫德人的吗？他们曾凿开山岳的岩石，用石块筑家，</p>"
        },
        "10": {
            "verses": {
                "89:10": {
                    "id": 10
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>难道你没有看到你主是怎样惩罚仗势欺人的法老的吗？</p>"
        },
        "11": {
            "verses": {
                "89:11": {
                    "id": 11
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>所有这些人都过分自大和不义，他们在城市不自量力。</p>"
        },
        "12": {
            "verses": {
                "89:12": {
                    "id": 12
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>他们以不信道和悖逆到处作恶。</p>"
        },
        "13": {
            "verses": {
                "89:13": {
                    "id": 13
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>故真主以严厉的刑罚惩治了他们，将他们从大地上铲除，</p>"
        },
        "14": {
            "verses": {
                "89:14": {
                    "id": 14
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>使者啊！你的主确是观察和监视人们的行为的，祂将以乐园奖赏行为优秀者，以火狱惩罚行为恶劣者。</p>"
        },
        "15": {
            "verses": {
                "89:15": {
                    "id": 15
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>“至于人类，其秉性就是当他的主考验他、优待他、恩赏他钱财、子嗣和荣耀时，他认为这是真主对他的优待，故他说‘我的主优待我，是因为我值得祂优待。’</p>"
        },
        "16": {
            "verses": {
                "89:16": {
                    "id": 16
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>而当他的主考验他、缩紧他的给养时，他认为这是真主对他的怠慢，故他说‘我的主怠慢我。’”</p>"
        },
        "17": {
            "verses": {
                "89:17": {
                    "id": 17
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>不然！事情不是人们想象的，恩惠证明真主对仆人的喜悦、惩罚证明真主对仆人的凌辱。而事实上是他们不以真主赐予他们的优待孤儿。</p>"
        },
        "18": {
            "verses": {
                "89:18": {
                    "id": 18
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>他们相互间也不嘱托为没有口粮的穷人提供食物，</p>"
        },
        "19": {
            "verses": {
                "89:19": {
                    "id": 19
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>你们残忍的吞噬弱势妇女和孤儿的权利，毫不顾及其解决途径，</p>"
        },
        "20": {
            "verses": {
                "89:20": {
                    "id": 20
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>你们酷爱钱财，故你们吝啬为主道施舍，以便将其敛为己有。</p>"
        },
        "21": {
            "verses": {
                "89:21": {
                    "id": 21
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>你们的行为不应该是这样的，你们当铭记当大地被摇动发生地震的时候，</p>"
        },
        "22": {
            "verses": {
                "89:22": {
                    "id": 22
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>使者啊！当你的主来甄别众仆之时，众天使列队排起的时候。</p>"
        },
        "23": {
            "verses": {
                "89:23": {
                    "id": 23
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>那日，火狱被带来，它有七万条缰绳，每条缰绳由七万个天使拉着。在那日，人们将记起对真主的疏忽，那日的记起对他又有什么益裨呢？那是报酬的日子，而非功修的日子。</p>"
        },
        "24": {
            "verses": {
                "89:24": {
                    "id": 24
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>他们非常懊悔地说：“但愿我曾为我真实的生活-后世的生活行过善事。”</p>"
        },
        "25": {
            "verses": {
                "89:25": {
                    "id": 25
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>那日，任何处罚都不像真主的惩罚，因为真主的惩罚是严厉的，是持久的。</p>"
        },
        "26": {
            "verses": {
                "89:26": {
                    "id": 26
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>任何人不会像不信道者那样被锁链束缚。</p>"
        },
        "27": {
            "verses": {
                "89:27": {
                    "id": 27
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>至于信士的灵魂，在它死亡和复活日时，有个声音对它说‘安定于信仰和善行的灵魂啊！</p>"
        },
        "28": {
            "verses": {
                "89:28": {
                    "id": 28
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>你当因获取的巨大赏赐而喜悦地回归你的主，当因所行的善功而被喜悦地回归你的主。</p>"
        },
        "29": {
            "verses": {
                "89:29": {
                    "id": 29
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>当进入我清廉的仆人之列，</p>"
        },
        "30": {
            "verses": {
                "89:30": {
                    "id": 30
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>当和他们一起进入我为他们预备的乐园。’”</p>"
        }
    }
}